name: Dinosaur Prehistoric Hunter VR
summary: Step into a breathtaking prehistoric world where you become the hunter. In Dinosaur Prehistoric Hunter VR, you’ll face off against nine unique dinosaur species, including the legendary T-Rex. Use a variety of weapons like the MP5, shotgun, handgun, bow and arrow, or even a sword to survive intense encounters. Designed with highly realistic graphics and immersive sound, this VR experience brings the thrill of dinosaur hunting to life like never before.
